Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.98,0:00:11.60,op_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}その意思は膝を立てる
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.27,0:00:20.36,op_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}wow wow wow...
