Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.94,0:00:32.43,op_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}進むべきは闇か?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.03,0:00:37.92,op_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}Knife 突き立てた先に
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.07,0:00:41.80,op_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}正体の見えぬ感情
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.99,0:00:47.61,op_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}-今はまだここで終われない-
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.61,0:00:52.75,op_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}ならば生きる準備をしろよ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.87,0:00:58.00,op_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}堆(うずたか)く積み上げてく熱情
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.00,0:01:02.57,op_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}重たいに決まってんだろう?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.47,0:01:03.82,op_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5\pos(640,660)}{\fad(200,200)}wake up your tough intention!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.95,0:01:08.20,op_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}未熟だと笑うが良いさ 戦場
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.20,0:01:14.83,op_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}一つずつ確かめてやるから
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.01,0:01:16.38,op_ja,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}…かかって来い{\fnSource Han Sans Medium}!
